Novartis to Cut Debt Before Making Large Purchases, Blick Says

-- B y   D e r m o t   D o h e r t y
-- 
2011-04-09T09:52:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/novartis-to-cut-debt-before-making-large-purchases-blick-says.html
Novartis AG (NOVN)  plans to further reduce
its debt before making “large” acquisitions, Blick reported,
citing Chairman Daniel Vasella.  Smaller purchases are still possible “in the near
future,” Vasella said in an interview in today’s  newspaper .  To contact the reporter on this story:
